name: Gyro Void Core
desc: the Gyro Core has been Replaced with a self containing Stable Void core,during shut down, care must be take to not Implode the ship.  .

name: Abritrator Compact Gantry
desc:
Compact Launch Bays that ease servicing Smaller Space Vehicles such as Arbitrators. Optimized Tooling and space Usage Allow the deck crew to manage %s for each Installed Arbitrator wing.

Those Specialized facilities do not offer any tangible benefit, nor drawback, when operating regular fighters and wanzers wings.
sModDesc: Once per combat, when the fighter replacement rate reaches %s, the fighter launch bays are switched to operate from a "B-deck". Standby fighters are launched to rapidly bring wings back to full strength, and the fighter replacement rate is set to %s.
